Model: d_recruiting
Schema: edm_recruiting_rpt
Database: EDW_DEV_SGU
Materialization: table
Description: 
Depends On: source.dbt_recruiting.edm_recruiting_rpt.fact_recruiting_event, model.dbt_recruiting.d_worker, model.dbt_recruiting.d_candidate, model.dbt_recruiting.d_office
SQL: {#
Jira         Date          Who                  Description
===================================================================================================================
 GWHD-2221    2024/05/02    Kulvinder Singh    create view for recruiting_dei
 GWHD-2221    2024/05/03    Kulvinder Singh    renamed the alias, made changes as discussed, can prefix added in all candidate
 GWHD-2281    2024/05/09    Kulvinder Singh    added isrehire in worker columns and worker ctes added as discussed with DA
 GWHD 2294    2024/05/15    Kulvinder Singh    renamed to D_RECRUITING
 GWHD-2294    2024/05/16    Kulvinder Singh    reordered D_CANDIDATE_COLUMNS
 GWHD-2388    2024/06/12    Kulvinder Singh    added CAN_GPA
 GWHD-2516    2024/07/03    Kulvinder Singh    removed wor_hist cols
 GWHD-2867    2024/07/03    Kulvinder Singh    removed additional_allocation_Address and external id also added worker_Capacity columns
 GWHD-2974    2024/10/10    Kulvinder singh     added new columns in Candidate(CAN_POSITIONID,CAN_JOB_POST_STARTDATE, CAN_JOB_POSITIONID,CAN_JOB_COHORT)
 GWHD-3865    2025/04/22    Kulvinder Singh    added worker_current_state_flag in place of current_flag
 GWHD-4140    2025/06/16    Kulvinder Singh    added can_profile_recruiter_external_id and the name and email from worker
#}
{{
    config(
        alias="D_RECRUITING",
        materialized="table",
        schema="edm_recruiting_rpt",
        tags=["d_recruiting"],
        copy_grants=true,
    )
}}

with
--get firstname, lastname and email from worker
cte_person_external_id as (
    select 
       person_external_id as wor_person_workerid, 
       preferedfirstname as wor_person_first_name, 
       preferredlastname as wor_person_last_name, 
       legalfirstname as wor_person_legal_first_name,
       legallastname as wor_person_legal_last_name,
       primaryworkemailaddress as wor_person_email
    from {{ref("d_worker")}} join {{ref("d_candidate")}}
    on  (d_worker.workerid=nvl(try_to_number(d_candidate.person_external_id),-1) and d_worker.workerid <> -1 and  d_worker.worker_current_state_flag='Y') and 
        (d_candidate.person_external_id is not null or  d_candidate.person_external_id <> '-1' ) and 
        d_candidate.person_external_id not like 'S_%' 
    group by all
),

cte_job_requisition_sourcer_id as (
    select 
       job_sourcer_external_id as wor_job_sourcer_workerid,
       preferedfirstname as wor_job_sourcer_first_name, 
       preferredlastname as wor_job_sourcer_last_name ,
       legalfirstname as wor_job_sourcer_legal_first_name,
       legallastname as wor_job_sourcer_legal_last_name
    from {{ref("d_worker")}} join {{ref("d_candidate")}}
    on  (d_worker.workerid=nvl(try_to_number(d_candidate.job_sourcer_external_id),-1) and d_worker.workerid <> -1 and d_worker.worker_current_state_flag='Y') and 
        (d_candidate.job_sourcer_external_id is not null or  d_candidate.job_sourcer_external_id <> '-1' ) and
        d_candidate.job_sourcer_external_id not like 'S_%' 
    group by all
),

cte_job_recruiter_id as (
    select 
       job_recruiter_external_id as wor_job_recruiter_workerid, 
       preferedfirstname as wor_job_recruiter_first_name, 
       preferredlastname as wor_job_recruiter_last_name , 
       legalfirstname as wor_job_recruiter_legal_first_name,
       legallastname as wor_job_recruiter_legal_last_name,
       primaryworkemailaddress as wor_job_recruiter_email
    from {{ref("d_worker")}} join {{ref("d_candidate")}}
    on  (d_worker.workerid=nvl(try_to_number(d_candidate.job_recruiter_external_id),-1) and d_worker.workerid <> -1 and d_worker.worker_current_state_flag='Y') and 
        (d_candidate.job_recruiter_external_id is not null or  d_candidate.job_recruiter_external_id <> '-1' ) and
        d_candidate.job_recruiter_external_id not like 'S_%' 
    group by all
),

cte_job_pa_sponser_id as (
    select 
       job_pa_sponsor_external_id as wor_job_pa_sponser_workerid, 
       preferedfirstname as wor_job_pa_sponser_first_name, 
       preferredlastname as wor_job_pa_sponser_last_name , 
       legalfirstname as wor_job_pa_sponser_legal_first_name,
       legallastname as wor_job_pa_sponser_legal_last_name
    from {{ref("d_worker")}} join {{ref("d_candidate")}}
    on  (d_worker.workerid=nvl(try_to_number(d_candidate.job_pa_sponsor_external_id),-1) and d_worker.workerid <> -1 and d_worker.worker_current_state_flag='Y') and 
        (d_candidate.job_pa_sponsor_external_id is not null or  d_candidate.job_pa_sponsor_external_id <> '-1' ) and
        d_candidate.job_pa_sponsor_external_id not like 'S_%' 
    group by all
),
cte_hiring_manager_id as (
    select 
       hiring_manager_external_id as wor_hiring_manager_workerid, 
       preferedfirstname as wor_hiring_manager_first_name, 
       preferredlastname as wor_hiring_manager_last_name ,
       legalfirstname as wor_hiring_manager_legal_first_name,
       legallastname as wor_hiring_manager_legal_last_name,
       primaryworkemailaddress as wor_hiring_manager_email
    from {{ref("d_worker")}} join {{ref("d_candidate")}}
    on  (d_worker.workerid=nvl(try_to_number(d_candidate.hiring_manager_external_id),-1) and d_worker.workerid <> -1 and d_worker.worker_current_state_flag='Y') and 
        (d_candidate.hiring_manager_external_id is not null or  d_candidate.hiring_manager_external_id <> '-1' ) and
        d_candidate.hiring_manager_external_id not like 'S_%' 
    group by all
),

cte_job_offer_recruiter_id as (
    select 
       can_job_offer_recruiter_external_id as wor_job_offer_recruiter_workerid, 
       preferedfirstname as wor_job_offer_recruiter_first_name, 
       preferredlastname as wor_job_offer_recruiter_last_name ,

left join cte_hist_job_recruiter_id on c.can_hist_recruiter_id=cte_hist_job_recruiter_id.wor_hist_job_recruiter_workerid
left join cte_hist_hiring_manager_id on c.can_hist_hrm_id=cte_hist_hiring_manager_id.wor_hist_hiring_manager_workerid
left join cte_profile_recruiter_id on c.can_profile_recruiter_external_id=cte_profile_recruiter_id.wor_profile_recruiter_workerid
left join cte_added_by_id on c.can_cp_added_by_external_id=cte_added_by_id.wor_added_by_workerid
left join cte_created_by_id on c.can_cp_created_by_external_id=cte_created_by_id.wor_created_by_workerid
left join cte_suggested_id on c.can_cp_suggested_external_id=cte_suggested_id.wor_suggested_workerid
left join {{ ref("d_office") }} off1 on fact.pkhash_office_job_requisition = off1.pkhash_office and off1.current_flag='Y'

left join {{ ref("d_office") }} off4 on fact.pkhash_office_can_job_offer_home = off4.pkhash_office and off4.current_flag='Y'
left join {{ ref("d_office") }} off5 on fact.pkhash_office_can_job_offer_host = off5.pkhash_office and off5.current_flag='Y'

text:
Model: fact_recruiting_event
Schema: edm_recruiting_rpt
Database: EDW_DEV_SGU
Materialization: table
Description: 
Depends On: model.dbt_recruiting.d_candidate, model.dbt_recruiting.d_office, model.dbt_recruiting.d_worker
SQL: {#
Jira         Date          Who                  Description
===================================================================================================================
GWHD-2089    2024/05/06    Kulvinder Singh      orignal code
GWHD 2294    2024/05/15    Kulvinder Singh      added the new join columns as discussed with DA and also updated the columns name from CAND
GWHD-2281    2024/05/21    Kulvinder Singh      replaced the placeholder of pkhash_assigned_application_office 
GWHD-3865    2025/04/22    Kulvinder Singh      added worker_current_state_flag in place of current_flag
#}
{{
  config(
      alias = 'fact_recruiting_event',
      materialized = 'table',
      schema = 'edm_recruiting_rpt',
      tags = ['fact_recruiting_load'],
      copy_grants = true
    )
}}

with 

cte_candidate as (
    select 
        pkhash_key as pkhash_candidate, 
        person_external_id, 
        --debug and revisit 
        -- SUBSTRING(wd_home_office_code, 0, 3) as wd_home_office_code,
        null as job_location,
        can_asgn_app_ofc_name as can_assigned_application_office_name,
        can_primary_office_preference,
        can_job_offer_home_office_name,
        can_job_offer_host_name 
    from {{ref("d_candidate")}}
),

cte_office as  (
    select 
        pkhash_office, 
        wd_loc_nm,
        wd_loc_cd
    from {{ref('d_office')}} where current_flag='Y'
),

cte_worker as (
    select 
        workerid,
        locationcd, 
        pkhash as pkhash_worker 
    from {{ref('d_worker')}} where worker_current_state_flag='Y'
),

cte_candidate_records as (
    select
        pkhash_candidate,
        person_external_id,
        -- wd_home_office_code,
        case 
            when pkhash_worker is null then '-1'
            else pkhash_worker end as pkhash_worker,
        case 
            when office.pkhash_office is null then '-1'
            else office.pkhash_office end as pkhash_office,
        case 
            when off1.pkhash_office is null then '-1'
            else off1.pkhash_office end as pkhash_office_job_requisition,
        case 
            when off2.pkhash_office is null then '-1'
            else off2.pkhash_office end as pkhash_office_assigned_application,
        case 
            when off3.pkhash_office is null then '-1'
            else off3.pkhash_office end as pkhash_office_job_application_primary,
        case 
            when off4.pkhash_office is null then '-1'
            else off4.pkhash_office end as pkhash_office_can_job_offer_home,
        case 
            when off5.pkhash_office is null then '-1'
            else off5.pkhash_office end as pkhash_office_can_job_offer_host,
        workerid
        from 
            cte_candidate left join
            --revisit
            -- cte_office on wd_home_office_code=wd_loc_cd left join
            cte_office off1 on cte_candidate.job_location=off1.wd_loc_nm left join
            cte_office off2 on cte_candidate.can_assigned_application_office_name=off2.wd_loc_nm left join
            cte_office off3 on cte_candidate.can_primary_office_preference=off3.wd_loc_nm left join
            cte_office off4 on cte_candidate.can_job_offer_home_office_name=off4.wd_loc_nm left join
            cte_office off5 on cte_candidate.can_job_offer_host_name=off5.wd_loc_nm left join
            cte_worker on workerid=nvl(try_to_number(person_external_id),-1) left join
            cte_office office on cte_worker.locationcd=office.wd_loc_cd
),

cte_worker_records as (
    select 
        pkhash_worker, 
        locationcd, 
        pkhash_office, 
        wd_loc_cd 
    from 
        cte_worker left join 
        cte_office on locationcd=wd_loc_cd
    where pkhash_worker not in (select distinct pkhash_worker from cte_candidate_records)
)

select 
    -1 as EFFECTIVEDATEKEY,
    -1 as EFFECTIVESEQNBR, 
    pkhash_candidate as PKHASH_CANDIDATE, 
    pkhash_worker as PKHASH_WORKER, 
    -1 as PKHASH_FINANCE, 
    pkhash_office as PKHASH_OFFICE,
    --pkhash office as prefix
    pkhash_office_job_requisition,
    pkhash_office_assigned_application,
    pkhash_office_job_application_primary,
    pkhash_office_can_job_offer_home,
    pkhash_office_can_job_offer_host,
    -1 as LATEARRIVINGDIMKEY1 ,
    -1 as LATEARRIVINGDIMKEY2, 
    -1 as LATEARRIVINGDIMKEY3, 
    -1 as LATEARRIVINGDIMKEY4, 
    -1 as LATEARRIVINGDIMKEY5, 
    -1 as METRIC1, 
    -1 as METRIC2, 
    -1 as METRIC3, 
    -1 as METRIC4, 
    -1 as METRIC5, 
    -1 as METRIC6,  
    -1 as METRIC7, 
    -1 as METRIC8, 
    -1 as METRIC9, 
    -1 as METRIC10, 
    current_timestamp as LOADDTS 
from cte_candidate_records

UNION 
select 
    -1 as EFFECTIVEDATEKEY, 
    -1 as EFFECTIVESEQNBR , 
    '-1' as PKHASH_CANDIDATE , 
    pkhash_worker as PKHASH_WORKER, 
    -1 as PKHASH_FINANCE, 
    pkhash_office as PKHASH_OFFICE,
    '-1' as pkhash_office_job_requisition,
    '-1' as pkhash_office_assigned_application,
    '-1' as pkhash_office_job_application_primary,
    '-1' as pkhash_office_can_job_offer_home,
    '-1' as pkhash_office_can_job_offer_host,
    -1 as LATEARRIVINGDIMKEY1, 
    -1 as LATEARRIVINGDIMKEY2, 
    -1 as LATEARRIVINGDIMKEY3, 
    -1 as LATEARRIVINGDIMKEY4, 
    -1 as LATEARRIVINGDIMKEY5, 
    -1 as METRIC1, 
    -1 as METRIC2, 
    -1 as METRIC3, 
    -1 as METRIC4, 
    -1 as METRIC5, 
    -1 as METRIC6, 
    -1 as METRIC7, 
    -1 as METRIC8, 
    -1 as  METRIC9, 
    -1 as METRIC10, 
    current_timestamp as LOADDTS 
from cte_worker_records

text:
Model: tara_sourcing_v
Schema: edm_recruiting_etl
Database: EDW_DEV_SGU
Materialization: view
Description: 
Depends On: source.dbt_recruiting.raw_recruiting_byod.stages_bin_approved_final_bins, source.dbt_recruiting.edm_recruiting_rpt.tara_base_layer, model.dbt_recruiting.d_worker_linemanager_hierarchy, model.dbt_recruiting.d_candidate_stages, model.dbt_recruiting.d_candidate_communities_stages, model.dbt_recruiting.d_recruiting, model.dbt_recruiting.d_candidate_communities_converted_applications, model.dbt_recruiting.tara_requisition
SQL: {#
Jira         Date          Who                  Description
===================================================================================================================
GWHD-4140    2025/06/27    Kulvinder Singh     ORIGNAL CODE
#}
{{
    config(
        alias="tara_sourcing",
        materialized="view",
        schema="edm_recruiting_etl",
        tags=[ "tara_sourcing_rpt"],
        copy_grants=true
    )
}}
with cte_linemanager_hierarchy as (
    select 
        workerid, 
        lm1_managed_start_date, 
        lm1_managed_end_date,
        linemanager1,
        lm2_managed_start_date, 
        lm2_managed_end_date,
        linemanager2,
        lm3_managed_start_date, 
        lm3_managed_end_date, 
        linemanager3
    from {{ref("d_worker_linemanager_hierarchy")}}
)
,
cte_stage_bins as (
    select 
        *
        exclude (
            _LINE,
            _FIVETRAN_SYNCED 
            )
    from {{source("raw_recruiting_byod","stages_bin_approved_final_bins")}}
    group by all
)

,cte_d_candidate_stages as (
    select * from {{ref("d_candidate_stages")}}
)

, cte_d_candidate_communities_stages as (
    select * from {{ref("d_candidate_communities_stages")}}
)

, cte_tara_base_layer as (
    select * from {{source("edm_recruiting_rpt","tara_base_layer")}}
)

, cte_d_recruiting as (
    select * from {{ref('d_recruiting')}}
)

, cte_converted_applications as (
    select * from {{ref('d_candidate_communities_converted_applications')}}
)

, cte_communities_stages_bins as (
    select 
        stages.can_profile_id,
        stages.can_application_id,
        stages.can_com_position_id,
        max(case 
            when bins.bins_approved='Community_Active Leads'
            then 1 
            else 0 end) as IS_CP_ACTIVE_LEADS,
        max(case 
            when bins.bins_approved='Community_Contacted'
            then 1 
            else 0 end) as IS_CP_CONTACTED,
        max(case 
            when  bins.bins_approved='Community_Screened Out'
            then 1 
            else 0 end) as IS_CP_SCREENED_OUT,
        max(case 
            when bins.bins_approved='Community_Not interested'
            then 1 
            else 0 end) as IS_CP_NOT_INTERESTED,
        max(case 
            when bins.bins_approved='Community_Screening'
            then 1 
            else 0 end) as IS_CP_SCREENING,
        max(case 
            when bins.bins_approved='Community_Invited To Apply'
            then 1 
            else 0 end) as IS_CP_INVITED_TO_APPLY,
        max(case 
            when bins.bins_approved='Community_In Req'
            then 1 
            else 0 end) as IS_CP_IN_REQ
    from cte_d_candidate_communities_stages stages 
    left join cte_stage_bins bins
    on stages.can_prev_stage=bins.current_stages
    group by all 
)
,
cte_communities_data as 
(
    select rec.can_application_id,
    rec.can_profile_id,
    rec.can_cp_name,
    rec.can_cp_community_type,
    rec.can_cp_position_id,
    rec.can_cp_created_by_external_id,
    rec.wor_created_by_name,
    rec.can_cp_status,
    rec.can_cp_added_by_external_id,
    rec.wor_added_by_name,
    hier1.linemanager1 as wor_added_by_lm1_name,
    hier1.linemanager2 as wor_added_by_lm2_name,
    hier1.linemanager3 as wor_added_by_lm3_name,
    coalesce(hier1.linemanager1 || ', ','') || 
    coalesce(hier1.linemanager2 || ', ','') ||  
    coalesce(hier1.linemanager2,'') as wor_added_by_lms,
    rec.can_cp_suggested_external_id,
    rec.wor_suggested_name,
    hier2.linemanager1 as wor_suggested_lm1_name,
    hier2.linemanager2 as wor_suggested_lm2_name,
    hier2.linemanager3 as wor_suggested_lm3_name,
    coalesce(hier2.linemanager1 || ', ','') || 
    coalesce(hier2.linemanager2 || ', ','') ||  
    coalesce(hier2.linemanager2,'') as wor_suggested_lms,
    rec.can_cp_current_stage,
    rec.can_current_stage,
    bins.bins_approved as CAN_CURRENT_STAGE_BIN, --replace with tara_current_Stage_bin
    app_bins.bins_approved as CAN_APP_CURRENT_STAGE_BIN,
    rec.can_cp_current_stage_ts,
    rec.can_current_stagets,
    datediff('days',can_cp_current_stage_ts,current_timestamp) as can_cp_days_in_current_stage,
    datediff('days',can_current_stagets,current_timestamp) as can_app_days_in_current_stage,
    rec.can_cp_first_stage_ts,
    is_cp_active_leads,
    is_cp_contacted,
    is_cp_screened_out,
    is_cp_not_interested,
    is_cp_screening,
    is_cp_invited_to_apply,
    is_cp_in_req
    from cte_d_recruiting rec    
    LEFT JOIN cte_linemanager_hierarchy hier1 
    on hier1.workerid=can_cp_added_by_external_id 
    AND rec.can_cp_first_stage_ts BETWEEN  hier1.lm1_managed_start_date  and hier1.lm1_managed_end_date
    AND rec.can_cp_first_stage_ts BETWEEN  hier1.lm2_managed_start_date  and hier1.lm2_managed_end_date
    AND rec.can_cp_first_stage_ts BETWEEN  hier1.lm3_managed_start_date  and hier1.lm3_managed_end_date
    LEFT JOIN cte_linemanager_hierarchy hier2 
    ON hier2.workerid=can_cp_suggested_external_id
    AND rec.can_cp_first_stage_ts BETWEEN  hier2.lm1_managed_start_date  and hier2.lm1_managed_end_date
    AND rec.can_cp_first_stage_ts BETWEEN  hier2.lm2_managed_start_date  and hier2.lm2_managed_end_date
    AND rec.can_cp_first_stage_ts BETWEEN  hier2.lm3_managed_start_date  and hier2.lm3_managed_end_date
    LEFT JOIN cte_stage_bins bins ON
    rec.can_cp_current_stage=bins.current_stages
    LEFT JOIN cte_stage_bins app_bins ON
    rec.can_current_stage=app_bins.current_stages
    LEFT JOIN cte_communities_stages_bins is_fields ON
    rec.can_application_id=is_fields.can_application_id and
    rec.can_profile_id=is_fields.can_profile_id
    WHERE rec.can_application_id is not null
)
,
cte_communities_all_stages as (
    select 
        can_application_id , 
        can_profile_id, 
        'Community' as tara_stage_type , 
        can_prev_stage as can_all_stage , 
        can_prev_stagets as can_all_stagets 
    from cte_d_candidate_communities_stages
)
, 
cte_communities_bin_entry_day as (
    select 
        can_application_id,
        can_profile_id,
        bins.bins_approved,
        min(can_all_stagets) as bin_entry_ts
    from cte_communities_all_stages stage
    left join cte_stage_bins bins
    on stage.can_all_stage=bins.current_stages
    group by all 
),

cte_communities_joined as (
    select 
        a.CAN_APPLICATION_ID,
        a.CAN_PROFILE_ID,
        a.CAN_CP_NAME,
        a.CAN_CP_COMMUNITY_TYPE,
        a.CAN_CP_POSITION_ID,
        a.CAN_CP_CREATED_BY_EXTERNAL_ID,
        a.WOR_CREATED_BY_NAME,
        a.CAN_CP_STATUS,
        a.CAN_CP_ADDED_BY_EXTERNAL_ID,
        a.WOR_ADDED_BY_NAME,
        a.WOR_ADDED_BY_LM1_NAME,
        a.WOR_ADDED_BY_LM2_NAME,
        a.WOR_ADDED_BY_LM3_NAME,
        a.WOR_ADDED_BY_LMS,
        a.CAN_CP_SUGGESTED_EXTERNAL_ID,
        a.WOR_SUGGESTED_NAME,
        a.WOR_SUGGESTED_LM1_NAME,
        a.WOR_SUGGESTED_LM2_NAME,
        a.WOR_SUGGESTED_LM3_NAME,
        a.WOR_SUGGESTED_LMS,
        a.CAN_CP_CURRENT_STAGE,
        a.CAN_CURRENT_STAGE_BIN,
        a.CAN_CP_CURRENT_STAGE_TS,
        a.CAN_CP_DAYS_IN_CURRENT_STAGE,
        a.CAN_CP_CURRENT_STAGE as CAN_CP_AP_CURRENT_STAGE,
        a.CAN_CURRENT_STAGE_BIN as CAN_CP_AP_CURRENT_BIN,
        a.CAN_CP_CURRENT_STAGE_TS AS CAN_CP_AP_CURRENT_STAGE_TS,
        a.CAN_CP_DAYS_IN_CURRENT_STAGE as CAN_CP_AP_DAYS_IN_CURRENT_STAGE,
        a.CAN_CP_FIRST_STAGE_TS,
        a.IS_CP_ACTIVE_LEADS,
        a.IS_CP_CONTACTED,
        a.IS_CP_SCREENED_OUT,
        a.IS_CP_NOT_INTERESTED,
        a.IS_CP_SCREENING,
        a.IS_CP_INVITED_TO_APPLY,
        a.IS_CP_IN_REQ,
        b.tara_stage_type, 
        b.can_all_stage,
        b.can_all_stagets,
        datediff('days',c.bin_entry_ts,current_timestamp) as can_cp_ap_days_in_current_bin
    from cte_communities_data a  
    join cte_communities_all_stages b
    on a.can_application_id=b.can_application_id 
    and a.can_profile_id=b.can_profile_id  
    left join cte_communities_bin_entry_day c 
    on a.can_application_id=c.can_application_id 
    and a.can_profile_id=c.can_profile_id 
    and a.CAN_CURRENT_STAGE_BIN=c.bins_approved
)

, cte_application_all_stages as (
    select 
        can_application_id , 
        can_profile_id, 
        'Application' as tara_stage_type, 
        can_prev_stage as can_all_stage , 
        can_prev_stagets as can_all_stagets  
    from cte_d_candidate_stages
)
,

cte_application_bin_entry_day as (
    select 
        can_application_id,
        b.bins_approved,
        min(can_all_stagets) as bin_entry_ts
    from cte_application_all_stages a
    left join cte_stage_bins b
    on a.can_all_stage=b.current_stages
    group by all 
)
,

cte_applications_joined as (
    select 
        a.CAN_APPLICATION_ID,
        a.CAN_PROFILE_ID,
        d.community_name as CAN_CP_NAME,
        d.Community_type CAN_CP_COMMUNITY_TYPE,
        d.CAN_CP_POSITION_ID,
        a.CAN_CP_CREATED_BY_EXTERNAL_ID,
        a.WOR_CREATED_BY_NAME,
        a.CAN_CP_STATUS,
        d.CAN_CP_ADDED_BY_EXTERNAL_ID,
        d.WOR_ADDED_BY_NAME,
        hier1.linemanager1 as wor_added_by_lm1_name,
        hier1.linemanager2 as wor_added_by_lm2_name,
        hier1.linemanager3 as wor_added_by_lm3_name,
        coalesce(hier1.linemanager1 || ', ','') || 
        coalesce(hier1.linemanager2 || ', ','') ||  
        coalesce(hier1.linemanager2,'') as wor_added_by_lms,
        a.CAN_CP_SUGGESTED_EXTERNAL_ID,
        a.WOR_SUGGESTED_NAME,
        a.WOR_SUGGESTED_LM1_NAME,
        a.WOR_SUGGESTED_LM2_NAME,
        a.WOR_SUGGESTED_LM3_NAME,
        a.WOR_SUGGESTED_LMS,
        a.CAN_CP_CURRENT_STAGE,
        a.CAN_CURRENT_STAGE_BIN,
        a.CAN_CP_CURRENT_STAGE_TS,
        a.CAN_CP_DAYS_IN_CURRENT_STAGE,
        a.CAN_CURRENT_STAGE as CAN_CP_AP_CURRENT_STAGE,
        a.CAN_APP_CURRENT_STAGE_BIN as CAN_CP_AP_CURRENT_STAGE_BIN,
        a.CAN_CURRENT_STAGETS as CAN_CP_AP_CURRENT_STAGE_TS,
        a.CAN_APP_DAYS_IN_CURRENT_STAGE as CAN_CP_AP_DAYS_IN_CURRENT_STAGE,
        d.cp_first_ts as CAN_CP_FIRST_STAGE_TS,
        e.IS_CP_ACTIVE_LEADS,
        e.IS_CP_CONTACTED,
        e.IS_CP_SCREENED_OUT,
        e.IS_CP_NOT_INTERESTED,
        e.IS_CP_SCREENING,
        e.IS_CP_INVITED_TO_APPLY,
        e.IS_CP_IN_REQ,
        b.tara_stage_type, 
        b.can_all_stage,
        b.can_all_stagets,
        datediff('days',c.bin_entry_ts,current_timestamp) as can_cp_ap_days_in_current_bin
        from cte_communities_data a  join cte_application_all_stages b
    on a.can_application_id=b.can_application_id  
    left join cte_application_bin_entry_day c 
    on a.can_application_id =c.can_application_id
    and a.CAN_APP_CURRENT_STAGE_BIN=c.bins_approved
    left join cte_converted_applications d 
    on a.can_application_id=d.can_application_id
    left join cte_communities_stages_bins e 
    on d.can_profile_id=e.can_profile_id 
    and d.can_cp_position_id=e.can_com_position_id
    LEFT JOIN cte_linemanager_hierarchy hier1 
    on hier1.workerid=d.can_cp_added_by_external_id 
    AND d.cp_first_ts BETWEEN  hier1.lm1_managed_start_date  and hier1.lm1_managed_end_date

text:
Model: d_candidate_profile_tags_v
Schema: edm_recruiting_etl
Database: EDW_DEV_SGU
Materialization: view
Description: 
Depends On: source.dbt_recruiting.edw_candidate_rpt.d_candidate_profile_tags, source.dbt_recruiting.edm_recruiting_rpt.d_worker, model.dbt_recruiting.d_candidate, model.dbt_recruiting.d_worker_work
SQL: {#
Jira         Date          Who                  Description
===================================================================================================================
GWHD-4018    2025/05/29    Kulvinder Singh     ORIGNAL CODE
#}
{{
    config(
        alias="d_candidate_profile_tags_v",
        materialized="view",
        schema="edm_recruiting_etl",
        tags=["edm_recruiting_rpt", "edw_candidate_rpt"],
        copy_grants=true
    )
}}
-- depends_on: {{ ref('d_candidate') }}
-- depends_on: {{ ref('d_worker_work') }}
with
    cte_d_candidate_profile_tags as (
        select {{dbt_utils.star(from=source("edw_candidate_rpt", "d_candidate_profile_tags"), relation_alias="d_candidate_profile_tags_view" ) }}
        from
            {{ source("edw_candidate_rpt", "d_candidate_profile_tags") }} d_candidate_profile_tags_view
    ),
    cte_active_worker as (
        select 
            workerid,
            preferedfirstname, 
            preferredlastname,
            trim(nvl(preferedfirstname,'')|| ' '|| nvl(preferredlastname,'')) as preferredname,
            primaryworkemailaddress 
        from {{ source("edm_recruiting_rpt", "d_worker") }}
        where worker_current_state_flag = 'Y'
    )

select 
    can.CAN_TAG_CREATED_TS,
    can.CAN_TAG_GROUPID,
    can.CAN_TAG_ID,
    can.CAN_TAG_POSITIONID,
    can.CAN_PROFILE_ID,
    can.CAN_TAG_TEXT,
    can.CAN_TAG_TYPE_NAME,
    can.CAN_TAG_SUBTYPE,
    can.CAN_TAG_URL,
    can.CAN_TAG_CREATOR_EXTERNAL_ID,
    wor.preferredname as WOR_TAG_CREATOR_NAME,
    wor.primaryworkemailaddress as WOR_TAG_CREATOR_EMAIL,
    can.PKHASH_KEY,
    sha2(
        array_to_string(
            array_construct(
            to_varchar(nvl(can.CAN_TAG_CREATED_TS,'-1')),
            to_varchar(nvl(can.CAN_TAG_GROUPID,'-1')),
            to_varchar(nvl(can.CAN_TAG_ID,'-1')),
            to_varchar(nvl(can.CAN_TAG_POSITIONID,'-1')),
            to_varchar(nvl(can.CAN_PROFILE_ID,'-1')),
            to_varchar(nvl(can.CAN_TAG_TEXT,'-1')),
            to_varchar(nvl(can.CAN_TAG_TYPE_NAME,'-1')),
            to_varchar(nvl(can.CAN_TAG_SUBTYPE,'-1')),
            to_varchar(nvl(can.CAN_TAG_URL,'-1')),
            to_varchar(nvl(can.CAN_TAG_CREATOR_EXTERNAL_ID,'-1')),
            to_varchar(nvl(wor.preferredname ,'-1')),
            to_varchar(nvl(wor.primaryworkemailaddress ,'-1')),
            to_varchar(nvl(can.PKHASH_KEY,'-1'))        
            ), 
            '^^^'
        )
    ) as row_hash_key
from cte_d_candidate_profile_tags can
left join cte_active_worker  wor on nvl(try_to_number(can.can_tag_creator_external_id),-1) =wor.workerid

text:
Model: d_candidate_regulatory_us_v
Schema: edm_recruiting_etl
Database: EDW_DEV_SGU
Materialization: view
Description: 
Depends On: source.dbt_recruiting.edw_candidate_regulatory.cr360_regulatory_us, source.dbt_recruiting.edm_recruiting_rpt.d_worker, model.dbt_recruiting.d_candidate, model.dbt_recruiting.d_worker_work
SQL: {#
Jira         Date          Who                  Description
===================================================================================================================
GWHD-3287    2024/12/05    Kulvinder Singh     ORIGNAL CODE
#}
{{
    config(
        alias="d_candidate_regulatory_us_v",
        materialized="view",
        schema="edm_recruiting_etl",
        tags=[ "edw_candidate_regulatory"],
        copy_grants=true
    )
}}
-- depends_on: {{ ref('d_candidate') }}
-- depends_on: {{ ref('d_worker_work') }}
with 
cte_cand_regulatory as (
        select  {{dbt_utils.star(from=source("edw_candidate_regulatory", "cr360_regulatory_us"), relation_alias="d_candidate_regulatory_view" ) }}
        from
            {{ source("edw_candidate_regulatory", "cr360_regulatory_us") }} d_candidate_regulatory_view
    ),
cte_worker as (
        select 
            workerid,
            legalfirstname,
            legallastname,
            legalname,
            row_number() over (partition by workerid order by terminationdt desc) as rn
        from {{ source("edm_recruiting_rpt", "d_worker") }} where worker_current_state_flag='Y'
    )
    
select 
    cand.*, 
    wor.workerid as wor_workerid, 
    wor.legalname as wor_legalname,
    wor.legalfirstname as wor_legalfirstname,
    wor.legallastname as wor_legallastname,
    recruiter.workerid as wor_recruiter_workerid,
    recruiter.legalname as wor_recruiter_legalname,
    recruiter.legalfirstname as wor_recruiter_legalfirstname,
    recruiter.legallastname as wor_recruiter_legallastname,
    hiring_manager.workerid as wor_hiring_manager_workerid,
    hiring_manager.legalname as wor_hiring_manager_legalname ,
    hiring_manager.legalfirstname as wor_hiring_manager_legalfirstname ,
    hiring_manager.legallastname as wor_hiring_manager_legallastname 
    from cte_cand_regulatory cand
    left join  cte_worker wor on  wor.workerid=nvl(try_to_number(cand.person_external_id),-1) 
    left join cte_worker recruiter on nvl(try_to_number(cand.JOB_RECRUITER_EXTERNAL_ID),-1)  = recruiter.workerid 
    left join cte_worker hiring_manager on nvl(try_to_number(cand.HIRING_MANAGER_EXTERNAL_ID),-1)  = hiring_manager.workerid

        )
    ) as row_hash_key
from cte_d_candidate_communities_stages can
left join cte_active_worker  wor on nvl(try_to_number(can.can_cp_added_by_external_id),-1) =wor.workerid

name: d_worker_linemanager_hierarchy_v
text:
Model: d_worker_linemanager_hierarchy_v
Schema: edm_recruiting_etl
Database: EDW_DEV_SGU
Materialization: view
Description: 
Depends On: source.dbt_recruiting.edm_recruiting_rpt.d_worker_linemanager, source.dbt_recruiting.edm_recruiting_rpt.d_worker, model.dbt_recruiting.d_worker_work
SQL: {#
Jira         Date          Who                  Description
===================================================================================================================
GWHD-3262   2024/11/15    Kulvinder Singh     Orignal Code
#}
{{
    config(
        alias="D_WORKER_LINEMANAGER_HIERARCHY_V",
        materialized="view",
        schema="edm_recruiting_etl",
        tags=["edm_recruiting_rpt_linemanager"],
        copy_grants=true,
    )
}}

-- depends_on: {{ ref('d_worker_work') }}



with cte_linemanager as (
select WORKERWID, 
        WORKERID, 
        LEGALNAME, 
        SUPERVISORYORGMANAGER, 
        MANAGEDFROM, 
        CASE WHEN MANAGEDTO is null then '9999-12-31'
        else MANAGEDTO end as MANAGEDTO, 
        -- BUSINESSPROCESSTIME, 
        -- ROW_HASH_KEY, 
        SUPERVISORYORGMANAGERID from {{ source("edm_recruiting_rpt", "d_worker_linemanager") }}
),
cte_worker as (
    select * from {{ source("edm_recruiting_rpt", "d_worker") }} where current_flag='Y'
)


select e.workerid, 
e.workerwid,
e.legalname,
w.hiredt,
w.terminationdt,
w.businesstitle,
w.jobprofilenm,
w.jobfamilynm,
e.supervisoryorgmanager as linemanager1, 
m1.workerid as lm1_workerid, 
e.managedfrom as lm1_managed_start_date, 
e.managedto as lm1_managed_end_date,
m1.supervisoryorgmanager as linemanager2,
m2.workerid as lm2_workerid, 
m1.managedfrom as lm2_managed_start_date, 
m1.managedto as lm2_managed_end_date,
m2.supervisoryorgmanager as linemanager3,
m3.workerid as lm3_workerid, 
m2.managedfrom as lm3_managed_start_date, 
m2.managedto as lm3_managed_end_date,
m3.supervisoryorgmanager as linemanager4,
m3.supervisoryorgmanagerid as lm4_workerid, 
m3.managedfrom as lm4_managed_start_date, 
m3.managedto as lm4_managed_end_date ,
sha2(
        array_to_string(
            array_construct(to_varchar(concat(
                e.workerid, '^', 
                e.workerwid, '^', 
                lm1_workerid, '^', 
                lm1_managed_start_date,'^',
                lm1_managed_end_date,'^',
                lm2_workerid, '^', 
                lm2_managed_start_date,'^',
                lm2_managed_end_date,'^',
                lm3_workerid, '^', 
                lm3_managed_start_date,'^',
                lm3_managed_end_date,'^',
                lm4_workerid,'^',
                lm4_managed_start_date,'^',
                lm4_managed_end_date
                ))),
            '^^^'
        )
    ) as pkhash,
    
    -- row_hash_key including all specified columns
    sha2(
        array_to_string(
            array_construct(
                to_varchar(nvl(e.workerid, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(e.workerwid, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(e.legalname, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(w.hiredt, '1-JAN-1900')),
                to_varchar(nvl(w.terminationdt, '1-JAN-1900')),
                to_varchar(nvl(w.businesstitle, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(w.jobprofilenm, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(w.jobfamilynm, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(e.supervisoryorgmanager, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(e.workerid, '-1')),  -- lm1_workerid
                to_varchar(nvl(e.managedfrom, '1-JAN-1900')),  -- lm1_manage_start_date
                to_varchar(nvl(e.managedto, '1-JAN-1900')),  -- lm1_manage_end_date
                to_varchar(nvl(m1.supervisoryorgmanager, '-1')),  -- linemanager2
                to_varchar(nvl(m2.workerid, '-1')),  -- lm2_workerid
                to_varchar(nvl(m1.managedfrom, '1-JAN-1900')),  -- lm2_manage_start_date
                to_varchar(nvl(m1.managedto, '1-JAN-1900')),  -- lm2_manage_end_date
                to_varchar(nvl(m2.supervisoryorgmanager, '-1')),  -- linemanager3
                to_varchar(nvl(m3.workerid, '-1')),  -- lm3_workerid
                to_varchar(nvl(m2.managedfrom, '1-JAN-1900')),  -- lm3_manage_start_date
                to_varchar(nvl(m2.managedto, '1-JAN-1900')),  -- lm3_manage_end_date
                to_varchar(nvl(m3.supervisoryorgmanager, '-1')),  -- linemanager4
                to_varchar(nvl(m3.supervisoryorgmanagerid, '-1')),  -- lm4_workerid
                to_varchar(nvl(m3.managedfrom, '1-JAN-1900')),  -- lm4_manage_start_date
                to_varchar(nvl(m3.managedto, '1-JAN-1900'))  -- lm4_manage_end_date
            ), 
            '^^^'
        )
    ) as row_hash_key
from cte_linemanager e 
left join cte_worker w on e.workerid=w.workerid and e.workerwid=w.workerwid
left join cte_linemanager m1 on e.SUPERVISORYORGMANAGERID=m1.workerid 
    and ( m1.managedfrom<=e.managedto and m1.managedto>=e.managedfrom) 
left join cte_linemanager m2 on m1.SUPERVISORYORGMANAGERID=m2.workerid
    and( m2.managedfrom<=e.managedto and m2.managedto>=e.managedfrom )
left join cte_linemanager m3 on m2.SUPERVISORYORGMANAGERID=m3.workerid
    and( m3.managedfrom<=e.managedto and m3.managedto>=e.managedfrom )
order by e.managedfrom desc, m1.managedfrom desc
, m2.managedfrom desc, m3.managedfrom desc

        from

        select 
            workerid,
            preferedfirstname, 
            preferredlastname,
            trim(nvl(preferedfirstname,'')|| ' '|| nvl(preferredlastname,'')) as preferredname,
            primaryworkemailaddress 
        from {{ source("edm_recruiting_rpt", "d_worker") }}

    can.can_profile_id,

        array_to_string(
            array_construct(
                to_varchar(nvl(can.can_profile_id, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(can.can_application_id, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(can.can_enc_id, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(can.can_prev_stage, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(can.can_prev_stagets, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(can.can_com_position_id, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(can.dwh_last_updated, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(can.recruiter_external_id, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(wor_recruiter_name, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(wor_recruiter_email, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(can.pkhash_key, '-1'))          
            ), 
            '^^^'
        )
    ) as row_hash_key
from cte_d_candidate_communities_stages can
left join cte_active_worker  wor on nvl(try_to_number(can.recruiter_external_id),-1) =wor.workerid

name: tara_funnel_v
text:
Model: tara_funnel_v
Schema: edm_recruiting_etl
Database: EDW_DEV_SGU
Materialization: view
Description: 
Depends On: source.dbt_recruiting.raw_recruiting_byod.stages_bin_approved_final_bins, source.dbt_recruiting.edm_recruiting_rpt.d_candidate_stages, source.dbt_recruiting.edm_recruiting_rpt.tara_base_layer
SQL: {#
Jira         Date          Who                  Description
===================================================================================================================
GWHD-3655    2025/04/11    Kulvinder Singh     ORIGNAL CODE
#}
{{
    config(
        alias="tara_funnel",
        materialized="view",
        schema="edm_recruiting_etl",
        tags=[ "tara_funnel_rpt"],
        copy_grants=true
    )
}}

with cte_stage_bins as (
    select 
        *
        exclude (
            _LINE,
            _FIVETRAN_SYNCED 
            )
    from {{source("raw_recruiting_byod","stages_bin_approved_final_bins")}}
    group by all
)



,cte_d_candidate_stages as (
    select * from {{source("edm_recruiting_rpt","d_candidate_stages")}}
)

,cte_tara_base_layer as (
    select * from {{source("edm_recruiting_rpt","tara_base_layer")}}
    where can_application_id not like '%-%' 
    --this is not an ideal filter to seperate the communities data. prone to failure
)

,cte_candidate_stages_bin as (
    select 
        stg.can_application_id,
        stg.can_prev_stage,
        bins.bins_approved        
    from cte_d_candidate_stages stg left join
    cte_stage_bins bins on stg.can_prev_stage = bins.current_stages
)

,cte_stage_merged_ts as (
    SELECT
        STG.CAN_APPLICATION_ID,
        STG.CAN_ATS_ID,
        STG.CAN_PROFILE_ID,
        STG.CAN_JOB_ID,
        STG.CAN_PREV_STAGE,
        min(CAN_PREV_STAGETS) as CAN_PREV_STAGETS
    FROM
    cte_d_candidate_stages stg
    group by all
)

, cte_data_prep AS (
    SELECT
        STG.CAN_APPLICATION_ID,
        STG.CAN_ATS_ID,
        STG.CAN_PROFILE_ID,
        STG.CAN_JOB_ID,
        STG.CAN_PREV_STAGE,
        STG.CAN_PREV_STAGETS,
        LEAD(STG.CAN_PREV_STAGETS) OVER 
            (
                PARTITION BY STG.CAN_APPLICATION_ID, STG.CAN_PROFILE_ID
                ORDER BY STG.CAN_PREV_STAGETS
                ) as next_Stage_ts,
        DATEDIFF( 'day', STG.CAN_PREV_STAGETS, 
            case when 
                LEAD(STG.CAN_PREV_STAGETS) OVER 
                    (
                    PARTITION BY STG.CAN_APPLICATION_ID, STG.CAN_PROFILE_ID
                    ORDER BY STG.CAN_PREV_STAGETS
                    )
                is null then current_timestamp
            else 
                LEAD(STG.CAN_PREV_STAGETS) OVER 
                    (
                    PARTITION BY STG.CAN_APPLICATION_ID, STG.CAN_PROFILE_ID
                    ORDER BY STG.CAN_PREV_STAGETS
                    )
            end
                ) AS days
    FROM
    cte_stage_merged_ts STG 
)

, cte_interview_stage_funnel AS (
    SELECT
        CAN_APPLICATION_ID,
        IFNULL(MAX(CASE WHEN CAN_PREV_STAGE IN ('Interview - Interview R1') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END),0) as IS_INTERVIEW_R1,
        IFNULL(MAX(CASE WHEN CAN_PREV_STAGE IN ('Interview - Interview R1') THEN days ELSE 0 END),0) as DAYS_IN_INTERVIEW_R1,
        MIN(CASE WHEN CAN_PREV_STAGE IN ('Interview - Interview R1') then can_prev_Stagets else null end) as DATE_ENTER_INTERVIEW_R1,
        MAX(CASE WHEN CAN_PREV_STAGE IN ('Interview - Interview R1') then next_Stage_ts else null end) as DATE_EXIT_INTERVIEW_R1,
        IFNULL(MAX(CASE WHEN CAN_PREV_STAGE IN ('Interview - Interview R2') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END),0) as IS_INTERVIEW_R2,
        IFNULL(MAX(CASE WHEN CAN_PREV_STAGE IN ('Interview - Interview R2') THEN days ELSE 0 END),0) as DAYS_IN_INTERVIEW_R2,
        MIN(CASE WHEN CAN_PREV_STAGE IN ('Interview - Interview R2') then can_prev_Stagets else null end) as DATE_ENTER_INTERVIEW_R2,
        MAX(CASE WHEN CAN_PREV_STAGE IN ('Interview - Interview R2') then next_Stage_ts else null end) as DATE_EXIT_INTERVIEW_R2,
        IFNULL(MAX(CASE WHEN CAN_PREV_STAGE IN ('Interview - Interview R3') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END),0) as IS_INTERVIEW_R3,
        IFNULL(MAX(CASE WHEN CAN_PREV_STAGE IN ('Interview - Interview R3') THEN days ELSE 0 END),0) as DAYS_IN_INTERVIEW_R3,
        MIN(CASE WHEN CAN_PREV_STAGE IN ('Interview - Interview R3') then can_prev_Stagets else null end) as DATE_ENTER_INTERVIEW_R3,
        MAX(CASE WHEN CAN_PREV_STAGE IN ('Interview - Interview R3') then next_Stage_ts else null end) as DATE_EXIT_INTERVIEW_R3,
        IFNULL(MAX(CASE WHEN CAN_PREV_STAGE IN ('Interview - Interview Final Round') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END),0) as IS_INTERVIEW_FR,
        IFNULL(MAX(CASE WHEN CAN_PREV_STAGE IN ('Interview - Interview Final Round') THEN days ELSE 0 END),0) as DAYS_IN_INTERVIEW_FR,
        MIN(CASE WHEN CAN_PREV_STAGE IN ('Interview - Interview Final Round') then can_prev_Stagets else null end) as DATE_ENTER_INTERVIEW_FR,
        MAX(CASE WHEN CAN_PREV_STAGE IN ('Interview - Interview Final Round') then next_Stage_ts else null end) as DATE_EXIT_INTERVIEW_FR
    FROM
    cte_data_prep
    GROUP BY
    CAN_APPLICATION_ID,
    CAN_ATS_ID
    ORDER BY CAN_APPLICATION_ID ASC
)

,cte_merged_data_bin_level as (
    select 
        stg.can_application_id,
        stg.can_ats_id,
        stg.can_profile_id,
        stg.can_job_id,
        bins.bins_approved,
        bins.bins_order,
        bins.reject_bucket,
        min(stg.can_prev_stagets) as can_prev_stagets
    from cte_d_candidate_stages stg
    LEFT JOIN cte_stage_bins BINS ON stg.can_prev_stage = bins.current_stages
    group by all 
)

,cte_data_prep_bin_level AS (
    SELECT
        STG.CAN_APPLICATION_ID,
        STG.CAN_ATS_ID,
        STG.CAN_PROFILE_ID,
        STG.CAN_JOB_ID,
        STG.BINS_APPROVED,
        STG.REJECT_BUCKET,
        STG.CAN_PREV_STAGETS,
        LEAD(STG.CAN_PREV_STAGETS) OVER 
                (
                PARTITION BY STG.CAN_APPLICATION_ID, STG.CAN_PROFILE_ID
                ORDER BY STG.CAN_PREV_STAGETS,bins_order
                ) as next_Stage_ts,
        LEAD(STG.BINS_APPROVED) OVER (
            PARTITION BY STG.CAN_APPLICATION_ID, STG.CAN_PROFILE_ID
            ORDER BY STG.CAN_PREV_STAGETS,bins_order
        ) AS next_val,
        CASE
            WHEN STG.BINS_APPROVED IN ('hired', 'reject') THEN NULL
            ELSE DATEDIFF(
            'day',
            STG.CAN_PREV_STAGETS,
            case when 
                    LEAD(STG.CAN_PREV_STAGETS) OVER 
                        (
                        PARTITION BY STG.CAN_APPLICATION_ID, STG.CAN_PROFILE_ID
                        ORDER BY STG.CAN_PREV_STAGETS,bins_order
                        )
                    is null then current_timestamp
                else 
                    LEAD(STG.CAN_PREV_STAGETS) OVER 
                        (
                        PARTITION BY STG.CAN_APPLICATION_ID, STG.CAN_PROFILE_ID
                        ORDER BY STG.CAN_PREV_STAGETS,bins_order
                        )
                end
        )
        END AS days
    FROM
    cte_merged_data_bin_level STG
)

,cte_funnel_for_bins AS (
    SELECT
        CAN_APPLICATION_ID,
        CAN_ATS_ID,
        BINS_APPROVED,
        MIN(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED IN ('apply') then can_prev_Stagets else null end) as DATE_ENTER_APPLY,
        MIN(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED IN ('assessment') then can_prev_Stagets else null end) as DATE_ENTER_ASSESSMENT,
        MIN(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED IN ('screen') then can_prev_Stagets else null end) as DATE_ENTER_SCREEN,
        MIN(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED IN ('interview') then can_prev_Stagets else null end) as DATE_ENTER_INTERVIEW,
        MIN(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED IN ('Offer Extend') then can_prev_Stagets else null end) as DATE_ENTER_OE,
        MIN(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED IN ('Offer Accept') then can_prev_Stagets else null end) as DATE_ENTER_OA,
        MAX(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED IN ('apply') then next_Stage_ts else null end) as DATE_EXIT_APPLY,
        MIN(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED IN ('assessment') then can_prev_Stagets else null end) as DATE_EXIT_ASSESSMENT,
        MAX(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED IN ('screen') then next_Stage_ts else null end) as DATE_EXIT_SCREEN,
        MAX(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED IN ('interview') then next_Stage_ts else null end) as DATE_EXIT_INTERVIEW,
        MAX(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED IN ('Offer Extend') then next_Stage_ts else null end) as DATE_EXIT_OE,
        MAX(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED IN ('Offer Accept') then next_Stage_ts else null end) as DATE_EXIT_OA,
        SUM(days) AS total_days,
        count(1) as stage_count
    FROM
    cte_data_prep_bin_level
    GROUP BY
    CAN_APPLICATION_ID,
    CAN_ATS_ID,
    BINS_APPROVED
    ORDER BY CAN_APPLICATION_ID ASC
)

, cte_funnel_grouping_for_bins as (
    SELECT
        CAN_APPLICATION_ID,
        CAN_ATS_ID,
        MAX(DATE_ENTER_APPLY) as DATE_ENTER_APPLY,
        MAX(DATE_EXIT_APPLY) as DATE_EXIT_APPLY,
        IFNULL(MAX(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED = 'apply' THEN total_days END),0) AS DAYS_STAGE_APPLY,
        MAX(DATE_ENTER_ASSESSMENT) as DATE_ENTER_ASSESSMENT,
        MAX(DATE_EXIT_ASSESSMENT) as DATE_EXIT_ASSESSMENT,
        IFNULL(MAX(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED = 'assessment' THEN total_days END),0) AS DAYS_STAGE_ASSESSMENT,
        MAX(DATE_ENTER_SCREEN) as DATE_ENTER_SCREEN,
        MAX(DATE_EXIT_SCREEN) as DATE_EXIT_SCREEN,
        IFNULL(MAX(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED = 'screen' THEN total_days END),0) AS DAYS_STAGE_SCREEN,
        MAX(DATE_ENTER_INTERVIEW) as DATE_ENTER_INTERVIEW,
        MAX(DATE_EXIT_INTERVIEW) as DATE_EXIT_INTERVIEW,
        IFNULL(MAX(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED = 'interview' THEN total_days END),0) AS DAYS_STAGE_INTERVIEW,
        MAX(DATE_ENTER_OA) as DATE_ENTER_OA,
        MAX(DATE_EXIT_OA) as DATE_EXIT_OA,
        IFNULL(MAX(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED IN ('Offer Accept', 'pre-hire') THEN total_days END),0) AS DAYS_STAGE_OFFER_ACCEPTED,
        MAX(DATE_ENTER_OE) as DATE_ENTER_OE,
        MAX(DATE_EXIT_OE) as DATE_EXIT_OE,
        IFNULL(MAX(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED = 'Offer Extend' THEN total_days END),0) AS DAYS_STAGE_OFFER_EXTEND
    FROM
    cte_funnel_for_bins
    GROUP BY all
)

text:
Model: tara_interview_feedback_v
Schema: edm_recruiting_etl

Description: 
Depends On: source.dbt_recruiting.raw_recruiting_byod.educational_mapping_education_background, model.dbt_recruiting.tara_base_layer, model.dbt_recruiting.d_candidate_profile_feedbacks_detail, model.dbt_recruiting.d_candidate_profile_feedbacks, model.dbt_recruiting.d_user_calendar_events, model.dbt_recruiting.d_user_calendar_interviewer_details, model.dbt_recruiting.d_user_calendar_interviewer_slots, model.dbt_recruiting.d_office, model.dbt_recruiting.d_worker
SQL: {#
Jira         Date          Who                  Description
===================================================================================================================
GWHD-3885    2025/04/29    Kulvinder Singh     ORIGNAL CODE
#}
{{
    config(
        alias="tara_interview_feedback",
        materialized="view",
        schema="edm_recruiting_etl",
        tags=[ "tara_interview_feedback_rpt"],
        copy_grants=true
    )
}}

with cte_tara_base_layer as (
    select * from {{ref("tara_base_layer")}}
)

,cte_d_candidate_profile_feedback_details as (
    select * from {{ref("d_candidate_profile_feedbacks_detail")}}
)

,cte_d_candidate_profile_feedbacks as (
    select * from {{ref("d_candidate_profile_feedbacks")}}
)

,cte_d_user_calendar_events as (
    select * from {{ref("d_user_calendar_events")}}
)

,cte_d_user_calendar_interviewer_details as (
    select * from {{ref("d_user_calendar_interviewer_details")}}
)

,cte_d_user_calendar_interviewer_slots as (
    select * from {{ref("d_user_calendar_interviewer_slots")}}
)


,cte_educational_mapping as (
    select 
        EDUCATIONAL_BACKGROUND_MAJOR_SUBJECT_LEVEL_1, 
        EDUCATIONAL_BACKGROUND_MAJOR_SUBJECT_LEVEL_2 , 
        EDUCATIONAL_BACKGROUND_MAJOR_SUBJECT
     from {{source("raw_recruiting_byod","educational_mapping_education_background")}}
     group by all
)

,cte_d_office as (
    select * from {{ref("d_office")}} where current_flag='Y'
)

,cte_active_worker as (
    select 
        worker.workerid,
        worker.preferedfirstname, 
        worker.preferredlastname,
        worker.primaryworkemailaddress,
        case 
            when worker.preferedfirstname is not null or worker.preferredlastname is not null
                then TRIM(COALESCE(preferedfirstname,'')|| ' ' || COALESCE(preferredlastname,''))
            else NULL
        END as fullname,
        worker.businesstitle,
        worker.hiredt, 
        worker.originalhiredt,
        worker.businessesnm,
        worker.jobcategorynm,
        worker.gender,
        worker.locationnm ,
        worker.cohortstep, 
        worker.jobcohortclassificationid,
        worker.jobcohortclassificationnm,
        office.bcg_geo_region_cd, 
        office.bcg_geo_sys_nm
        
    from {{ref("d_worker")}} worker
    left join cte_d_office office 
    on worker.locationcd=office.wd_loc_cd
    where worker_current_state_flag = 'Y'
    
)

, cte_feedback_questions_pivoted AS (

        MAX(CASE WHEN new_label='Relevant_Experience' then new_score else null end) as Relevant_Experience,
        MAX(CASE WHEN new_label='Leadership_People_Development' then new_score else null end) as Leadership_People_Development,
        MAX(CASE WHEN new_label='Problem_Solving_&_Insight' then new_score else null end) as Problem_Solving_Insight,

        MAX(CASE WHEN new_label='Total_Score' then new_score else null end) as Total_Score
    FROM cte_feedback_questions
    GROUP BY FEEDBACKID 
)
,cte_final_feedback AS (
    SELECT 
        CPF.APPLICATION_ID,
        CPF.CREATEDAT AS CREATEDAT_FEEDBACK,
        CPF.USERCALENDAREVENTID,
        CPF.PLANNEDEVENTID AS PLANNEDEVENTID_FEEDBACK,
        CPF.FEEDBACKTEMPLATEID,
        CPF.FEEDBACKTEMPLATENAME,
        CASE
            WHEN CPF.FEEDBACKTEMPLATENAME like '%R1%' THEN 'Round 1 Feedback Forms:' 
            WHEN CPF.FEEDBACKTEMPLATENAME like '%R2%' THEN 'Round 2 Feedback Forms:'
            WHEN CPF.FEEDBACKTEMPLATENAME like '%R3%' THEN 'Round 3 Feedback Forms:'
            WHEN CPF.FEEDBACKTEMPLATENAME like '%Final Round%' THEN 'Final Round Feedback Forms'
            ELSE 'Other'
        END AS FEEDBACK_ROUNDS_FLAG,
        CASE
            WHEN CPF.FEEDBACKTEMPLATENAME like '%CT%' THEN 'CT' ELSE 'Other'
        END AS FEEDBACK_CT_FLAG,
        CPF.FEEDBACKTYPE,
        CPF.POSITIONID AS POSITIONID_FEEDBACK,
        CPF.PROFILEID,
        CPF.REQUESTEDAT,
        CPF.SUBMITTEDAT,
        CPF.REVIEWER_EXTERNAL_ID,
        reviewer.WORKERID as WOR_INTERVIEWER_WORKERID,
        reviewer.fullname as WOR_INTERVIEWER_NAME,
        reviewer.primaryworkemailaddress as WOR_INTERVIEWER_EMAIL,
        reviewer.gender as WOR_INTERVIEWER_GENDER,
        reviewer.businesstitle as WOR_INTERVIEWER_BUSINESSTITLE,
        reviewer.locationnm as WOR_INTERVIEWER_OFFICE,
        reviewer.bcg_geo_region_cd as WOR_INTERVIEWER_OFFICE_REGION,
        reviewer.bcg_geo_sys_nm as WOR_INTERVIEWER_OFFICE_SYSTEM,
        reviewer.businessesnm as WOR_INTERVIEWER_BUSINESSNM,
        reviewer.jobcategorynm as WOR_INTERVIEWER_JOBCATEGORYNM,
        reviewer.originalhiredt as WOR_INTERVIEWER_ORIGNALHIREDT,
        reviewer.hiredt as WOR_INTERVIEWER_HIREDT,
        reviewer.jobcohortclassificationnm as WOR_INTERVIEWER_JOBCOHORTCLASSIFICATIONNM,
        CPF.REQUESTER_EXTERNAL_ID,
        requester.workerid as WOR_REQUESTER_WORKERID,
        requester.fullname as WOR_REQUESTER_NAME,
        requester.primaryworkemailaddress as WOR_REQUESTER_EMAIL,
        CPF.STATUS AS STATUS_FEEDBACK,
        CPF.STAR_RATING,
        CPF.THUMBSUP_THUMBSDOWN,
        CFQ.* 
    FROM cte_d_candidate_profile_feedbacks CPF
    LEFT JOIN cte_feedback_questions_pivoted CFQ
    ON CPF.FEEDBACKID = CFQ.FEEDBACKID
    LEFT JOIN cte_active_worker reviewer    
    ON CPF.REVIEWER_EXTERNAL_ID=reviewer.WORKERID
    LEFT JOIN cte_active_worker requester    
    ON CPF.REQUESTER_EXTERNAL_ID=requester.WORKERID
    group by all
)
,cte_interview AS (
    SELECT 
        UCE.USER_EVENT_ID,
        UCE.APPLICATION_ID ,
        LOWER(UCE.ASSIGNEEUSERID) AS ASSIGNEEUSERID,
        UCE.plannedeventid AS PLANNEDEVENTID_INTERVIEW,
        UCE.CREATEDAT AS CREATEDAT_INTERVIEW,
        TO_TIMESTAMP_NTZ(UCIS.timeslot_start) as INTERVIEW_DATE,
        UCE.CAN_PROFILE_ID,
        UCE.POSITIONID AS POSITIONID_INTERVIEW,
        UCE.STATUS AS STATUS_INTERVIEW,
        UCE.creatoruserid,
        UCE.durationminutes,
        ucid.interviewer_external_id,
        ucid.interviewer_optional
    FROM cte_d_user_calendar_events UCE
    LEFT JOIN cte_d_user_calendar_interviewer_details ucid 
    ON UCE.USER_EVENT_ID = ucid.USER_EVENT_ID
    LEFT JOIN cte_d_user_calendar_interviewer_slots ucis 
    ON uce.USER_EVENT_ID=ucis.USER_EVENT_ID and ucid.slot_id=ucis.slot_id
    group by all
)

        NVL(feedback.COMMUNICATION_PRESENCE,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(feedback.COMPETENCY_EXPERTISE,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(feedback.EFFECTIVENESS_IMPACT,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(feedback.EFFECTIVENESS_VALUE_CREATION,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(feedback.EXPERTISE_IDEA_DEVELOPMENT,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(feedback.EXPERTISE,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(feedback.LEADERSHIP,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(feedback.CLIENT_INTERACTIONS_BILLABLE_ROLES,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(feedback.OVERALL_FEEDBACK_STAR_RATING,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(feedback.OVERALL_RATING,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(feedback.RELEVANT_EXPERIENCE,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(feedback.LEADERSHIP_PEOPLE_DEVELOPMENT,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(feedback.PROBLEM_SOLVING_INSIGHT,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(feedback.ROLE_MODEL,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(feedback.SCREENING_MARK,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(feedback.TEAMING_COLOBORATION,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(feedback.TECHNICAL_FUNCTIONAL_EXPERTISE,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(feedback.TOTAL_SCORE,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(interview.USER_EVENT_ID,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(interview.ASSIGNEEUSERID,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(interview.PLANNEDEVENTID_INTERVIEW,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(interview.CREATEDAT_INTERVIEW,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(interview.INTERVIEW_DATE,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(interview.POSITIONID_INTERVIEW,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(interview.STATUS_INTERVIEW,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(interview.CREATORUSERID,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(interview.DURATIONMINUTES,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(interview.INTERVIEWER_EXTERNAL_ID,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(interview.INTERVIEWER_OPTIONAL,'-1') , '^',
        NVL(TARA_Overall_rec_translated,'-1'),'^',
        NVL(TARA_IS_DUPLICATE,'-1'),'^',
        NVL(TARA_Feedback_Category_1,'-1'),'^', 
        NVL(TARA_Feedback_Category_2,'-1'),'^',
        PKHASH , '^' ))),'^^^')) as ROW_HASH_KEY
FROM cte_tara_base_layer base
inner JOIN cte_final_feedback feedback 
    ON base.CAN_APPLICATION_ID = feedback.APPLICATION_ID
LEFT JOIN cte_interview interview 
    ON interview.application_id= base.can_application_id
    and feedback.reviewer_external_id=interview.interviewer_external_id
LEFT JOIN cte_educational_mapping edu_background 
    ON base.can_job_app_recent_major=edu_background.educational_background_major_subject

name: d_candidate_job_v
text:
Model: d_candidate_job_v
Schema: edm_recruiting_etl
Database: EDW_DEV_SGU
Materialization: view
Description: 
Depends On: source.dbt_recruiting.edw_candidate_rpt.d_candidate_job, source.dbt_recruiting.edw_candidate_rpt.d_candidate_job_followers, source.dbt_recruiting.edm_recruiting_rpt.d_worker, model.dbt_recruiting.d_candidate, model.dbt_recruiting.d_worker_work
SQL: {#
Jira         Date          Who                  Description
===================================================================================================================
GWHD-3837    2025/04/10    Kulvinder Singh     ORIGNAL CODE
#}
{{
    config(
        alias="d_candidate_job_v",
        materialized="view",
        schema="edm_recruiting_etl",
        tags=["edm_recruiting_rpt", "edw_candidate_rpt"],
        copy_grants=true
    )
}}
-- depends_on: {{ ref('d_candidate') }}
-- depends_on: {{ ref('d_worker_work') }}
with
    cte_job as (
        select {{dbt_utils.star(from=source("edw_candidate_rpt", "d_candidate_job"), relation_alias="d_candidate_job_view" ) }}
        from
            {{ source("edw_candidate_rpt", "d_candidate_job") }} d_candidate_job_view
    ),
    cte_job_followers as (
        select {{dbt_utils.star(from=source("edw_candidate_rpt", "d_candidate_job_followers"), relation_alias="d_candidate_job_followers_view" ) }}
        from
            {{ source("edw_candidate_rpt", "d_candidate_job_followers") }} d_candidate_job_followers_view
    ),
    cte_active_worker as (
        select workerid,
        preferedfirstname,
        preferredlastname,
        legallastname,
        legalname,
        primaryworkemailaddress,
        trim(preferedfirstname|| ' ' || preferredlastname) as preferredname,
        from {{ source("edm_recruiting_rpt", "d_worker") }}
        where worker_current_state_flag = 'Y'
    ),
    cte_followers_name as (
        select 
            followers.job_id,
            LISTAGG(followers.followers_external_id, ', ') WITHIN GROUP(ORDER BY followers.followers_external_id) AS FOLLOWERS_ID,
            LISTAGG(worker.preferredname, ', ') WITHIN GROUP(ORDER BY worker.LEGALNAME) AS FOLLOWERS_NAMES
        from cte_job_followers followers
        left join cte_active_worker worker on
        try_to_number(followers.followers_external_id)=worker.workerid
        group by followers.job_id 
    )

select 
    job.job_id,
    job.latest_on_hold_date,
    job.first_approved_date,
    job.latest_closed_date,
    job.office_address_city,
    job.wd_position_ids,
    job.office_address_country,
    job.no_of_headcount,
    job.date_open,
    job.external_id,
    job.no_of_remaining_openings,
    job.bst_role,
    job.apply_flow,
    job.job_cost_center_id,
    job.job_primary_location_external_id,
    job.can_hist_hrm_id,
    job.hiring_manager_external_id,
    job.can_hist_recruiter_id,
    job.recruiter_external_id,
    ifnull(cur_recruiter.workerid, hist_recruiter.workerid) as wor_recruiter_workerid,
    case 
        when cur_recruiter.workerid is not null then cur_recruiter.preferredname
        else hist_recruiter.preferredname 
        end  as wor_recruiter_name,
    case 
        when cur_recruiter.workerid is not null then cur_recruiter.primaryworkemailaddress
        else hist_recruiter.primaryworkemailaddress 
        end  as wor_recruiter_email,
    followers.followers_id,
    followers.followers_names,
    job.pkhash_key,
    sha2(
        array_to_string(
            array_construct(
                to_varchar(nvl(job.job_id,'-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(job.latest_on_hold_date,'-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(job.first_approved_date,'-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(job.latest_closed_date,'-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(job.office_address_city,'-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(job.wd_position_ids,'-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(job.office_address_country,'-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(job.no_of_headcount,'-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(job.date_open,'-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(job.external_id,'-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(job.no_of_remaining_openings,'-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(job.bst_role,'-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(job.apply_flow,'-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(job.job_cost_center_id,'-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(job.job_primary_location_external_id,'-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(job.can_hist_hrm_id,'-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(job.hiring_manager_external_id,'-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(job.can_hist_recruiter_id,'-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(job.recruiter_external_id,'-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(followers.followers_id,'-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(followers.followers_names,'-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(job.pkhash_key,'-1'))   
            ), 
            '^^^'
        )
    ) as row_hash_key
from cte_job job
left join cte_followers_name  followers 
on job.job_id=followers.job_id 
left join cte_active_worker hist_recruiter 
on try_to_number(job.can_hist_recruiter_id)=hist_recruiter.workerid
left join cte_active_worker cur_recruiter 
on try_to_number(job.recruiter_external_id)=cur_recruiter.workerid

}}
-- depends_on: {{ ref('d_candidate') }}
-- depends_on: {{ ref('d_worker_work') }}
with
    cte_d_candidate_events as (
        select {{dbt_utils.star(from=source("edw_candidate_rpt", "d_candidate_events"), relation_alias="d_candidate_events_view" ) }}
        from
            {{ source("edw_candidate_rpt", "d_candidate_events") }} d_candidate_events_view
    ),

        select 
            workerid,
            preferedfirstname,

            trim(nvl(preferedfirstname,'')|| ' '|| nvl(preferredlastname,'')) as preferredname,
            primaryworkemailaddress 
        from {{ source("edm_recruiting_rpt", "d_worker") }}
        where worker_current_state_flag = 'Y'
    ),
    cte_joined as (
        select
            -- all event columns (except original ROW_HASH_KEY)
            b.events_start_timestamp,
            b.events_end_timestamp,
            b.events_planned_name,
            b.events_active_registrations,
            b.events_institution,
            b.events_venue,
            b.events_location_type,
            b.events_type,
            b.events_is_cancelled,
            b.events_is_published,
            b.events_planned_id,
            b.events_created_by_external_id,
            wor1.preferredname           as events_created_by_name,
            wor1.primaryworkemailaddress as events_created_by_email,
            b.events_createdat,
            b.events_status,
            b.events_selected_timezone,
            b.events_description,
            b.events_eventbucket,
            b.events_parentid,
            b.events_custom_internal_name,
            b.events_diversity_categorization,
            b.events_school_campus,
            b.events_custom_date_tbd,
            b.events_custom_charge_code,
            b.events_custom_business_unit_or_region,
            b.events_custom_host_business_unit,
            b.events_custom_contacts_external_id,
            wor2.preferredname           as events_custom_contacts_name,
            wor2.primaryworkemailaddress as events_custom_contacts_email,
            b.events_custom_ownership,
            b.events_custom_category,
            b.events_custom_target_audience,
            b.events_custom_target_audience_background,
            b.events_activity_type,
            b.events_activity_result,
            b.events_rsvpresponse,
            b.events_updated_by_external_id,
            wor3.preferredname           as events_updated_by_name,
            wor3.primaryworkemailaddress as events_updated_by_email,
            b.events_plannedevent_creator_external_id,
            wor4.preferredname           as events_plannedevent_creator_name,
            wor4.primaryworkemailaddress as events_plannedevent_creator_email,
            b.events_act_createdat,
            b.events_profileid,
            b.events_positionid,
            b.events_applicationid,
            b.eff_start_date,
            b.events_lastname,
            b.events_location,
            b.events_seniority_level,
            b.events_education_level,
            b.events_workexperience_years,
            b.events_firstname,
            b.events_atsentityid,
            b.events_experiences_work_title,
            b.events_efcustom_profile_office_location1,
            b.events_efcustom_profile_office_location2,
            b.events_efcustom_latest_education_major,
            b.events_efcustom_latest_education_school,
            b.events_efcustom_latest_education_degree,
            b.events_efcustom_latest_grad_date,
            b.dwh_last_updated,
            b.pkhash_key  
        from cte_d_candidate_events b
        left join cte_active_worker wor1
            on try_to_number(b.events_created_by_external_id) = wor1.workerid
        left join cte_active_worker wor2
            on try_to_number(b.events_custom_contacts_external_id) = wor2.workerid
        left join cte_active_worker wor3
            on try_to_number(b.events_updated_by_external_id) = wor3.workerid
        left join cte_active_worker wor4
            on try_to_number(b.events_plannedevent_creator_external_id) = wor4.workerid
        )
select
    cte_joined.*,
    -- include ALL projected fields in the hash
    sha2(
      array_to_string(
        array_construct(

          -- Event base fields
          to_varchar(coalesce(to_varchar(events_start_timestamp), '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(to_varchar(events_end_timestamp), '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_planned_name, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_active_registrations, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_institution, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_venue, '-1')),

          to_varchar(coalesce(events_type, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_is_cancelled, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_is_published, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(to_varchar(events_planned_id), '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_created_by_external_id, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(to_varchar(events_createdat), '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_status, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_selected_timezone, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_description, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_eventbucket, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_parentid, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_custom_internal_name, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_diversity_categorization, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_school_campus, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_custom_date_tbd, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_custom_charge_code, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_custom_business_unit_or_region, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_custom_host_business_unit, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_custom_contacts_external_id, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_custom_ownership, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_custom_category, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_custom_target_audience, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_custom_target_audience_background, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_activity_type, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_activity_result, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_rsvpresponse, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_updated_by_external_id, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_plannedevent_creator_external_id, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(to_varchar(events_act_createdat), '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(to_varchar(events_profileid), '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(to_varchar(events_positionid), '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(to_varchar(events_applicationid), '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(to_varchar(eff_start_date), '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_lastname, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_location, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_seniority_level, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_education_level, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_workexperience_years, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_firstname, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_atsentityid, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_experiences_work_title, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_efcustom_profile_office_location1, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_efcustom_profile_office_location2, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_efcustom_latest_education_major, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_efcustom_latest_education_school, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(events_efcustom_latest_education_degree, '-1')),

with
    cte_job_additional_followers as (
        select {{dbt_utils.star(from=source("edw_candidate_rpt", "d_candidate_job_additional_followers"), relation_alias="d_candidate_job_additional_followers_view" ) }}
        from
            {{ source("edw_candidate_rpt", "d_candidate_job_additional_followers") }} d_candidate_job_additional_followers_view
    ),
    cte_active_worker as (
        select workerid,
        legalfirstname,
        legallastname,
        legalname,
        primaryworkemailaddress,
        terminationdt,
        row_number() over (partition by workerid order by terminationdt desc) as rn
        from {{ source("edm_recruiting_rpt", "d_worker") }}
        where worker_current_state_flag = 'Y'
    )

select can.job_requisition_number, 
    can.job_id, 
    can.person_id, 
    can.person_external_id, 
    can.current_flag, 
    can.pkhash_key,
    wor.legalfirstname,
    wor.legallastname,
    wor.legalname,
    wor.primaryworkemailaddress,
    sha2(
        array_to_string(
            array_construct(
                to_varchar(nvl(can.job_requisition_number, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(can.job_id, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(can.person_id, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(can.person_external_id, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(can.current_flag, 'Y')),
                to_varchar(nvl(can.pkhash_key, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(wor.legalfirstname, 'UNKNOWN')),
                to_varchar(nvl(wor.legallastname, 'UNKNOWN')),
                to_varchar(nvl(wor.legalname, 'UNKNOWN')),
                to_varchar(nvl(wor.primaryworkemailaddress, 'UNKNOWN'))            
            ), 
            '^^^'
        )
    ) as row_hash_key
from cte_job_additional_followers can
left join cte_active_worker  wor on nvl(try_to_number(can.person_external_id),-1) =wor.workerid and rn=1

    NVL(profile_tag.IS_OA,'-1'),'^',

    NVL(HIRED_FLAG,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(reject_prev_stg.CAN_STAGE_PRIOR_REJECTION,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(IS_NATIVE,'-1'),'^'))),'^^^'))  as ROW_HASH_KEY
    -- recruiting.CAN_TAG_TEXT or recruiting.CAN_PROFILE_TAGS_COMBINED will come from cr360 mid april
from
cte_d_recruiting recruiting  
left join cte_profile_bin_tag profile_tag 
    on recruiting.can_application_id=profile_tag.can_application_id
left join cte_prev_reject_stages reject_prev_stg 
    on recruiting.can_application_id=reject_prev_stg.can_application_id
left join cte_gender lk_gender 
    on IFNULL(recruiting.can_pre_hire_gender,recruiting.can_profile_gender) = lk_gender.can_profile_gender
left join cte_allocation_mapping tm_alloc
    on  IFNULL(recruiting.CAN_JOB_OFFER_ALLOC1_NAME,recruiting.CAN_JOB_ALLOCATION1) = tm_alloc.allocation_union_rdm
left join cte_office_mapping_country_only off_coo
    ON office_tara = off_coo.office_in_rdm_ 
left join cte_d_office d_office
    ON office_tara =d_office.wd_loc_nm

Jira         Date          Who                  Description

    )
}}

with cte_d_candidate_group_events AS (
    SELECT
        EVENTS_PLANNED_NAME AS events_planned_group_name,
        EVENTS_PLANNED_ID   AS events_planned_parent_id
    FROM {{source("edm_recruiting_rpt","d_candidate_events")}}
    GROUP BY
        EVENTS_PLANNED_NAME,
        EVENTS_PLANNED_ID
)
,cte_d_candidate_events as (
    select * from {{source("edm_recruiting_rpt","d_candidate_events")}}
)

,cte_d_candidate_eventteam as (
    select * from {{source("edm_recruiting_rpt","d_candidate_eventteam")}}
)
,cte_d_worker as (
    SELECT
        DISTINCT
        workerid,
            preferedfirstname, 
            preferredlastname,
            trim(nvl(preferedfirstname,'')|| ' '|| nvl(preferredlastname,'')) as preferredname,
            primaryworkemailaddress,
            locationnm
    from {{ source("edm_recruiting_rpt", "d_worker") }}
)
,cte_eventteam_comma AS (
    SELECT
        et.eventteam_planned_event_id,
        LISTAGG(DISTINCT w.preferredname, ', ')     WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY w.preferredname) AS eventteam_names,
        LISTAGG(DISTINCT w.primaryworkemailaddress, ', ')    WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY w.primaryworkemailaddress) AS eventteam_emails,
		LISTAGG(DISTINCT w.locationnm, ', ')    WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY w.locationnm) AS eventteam_locations
    FROM cte_d_candidate_eventteam et
    LEFT JOIN cte_d_worker w
           ON et.eventteam_external_id = w.workerid
    --WHERE w.wor_currentrowind = 'Y'
    GROUP BY et.eventteam_planned_event_id
)
,cte_tara_base_layer as (
    select * from {{source("edm_recruiting_rpt","tara_base_layer")}}
    where can_application_id not like '%-%' 
    --this is not an ideal filter to seperate the communities data. prone to failure
)

        alias="tara_requisition",

    select * from {{source("edm_recruiting_rpt","d_candidate_job")}}
)

)

    select * from {{source("edm_recruiting_rpt","tara_base_layer")}}
)

    select * 
    from {{source("edm_recruiting_rpt","d_office")}} 
    where current_flag='Y'
)

,cte_can_job_source_grouped as (
    select CAN_JOB_ID,
        LISTAGG(DISTINCT CAN_SOURCE_NAME, ', ')
           WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY CAN_SOURCE_NAME) AS Concatenated_Sources
        FROM
        cte_tara_base_layer
        WHERE
        CAN_CURRENT_STAGE IN
        ('Hired - Workday Hire Success',
        'Hired - Workday Hire Success (Migrated)')
        AND CAN_SOURCE_NAME IS NOT NULL
        AND CAN_SOURCE_NAME <> ''
        GROUP BY CAN_JOB_ID

)

from 
cte_tara_base_layer base
left join cte_can_job_source_grouped job_sources
on base.can_job_id=job_sources.can_job_id

left join cte_business_mapping bm 
on ifnull(base.can_job_allocation1,base.can_job_allocation2)=bm.allocationnm

left join cte_business_function fm 
on base.can_job_cost_center_external_id=fm.costcenterid

left join cte_linemanager_hierarchy rec_lm 
on try_to_number(base.can_job_recruiter_external_id)=rec_lm.workerid
and base.can_job_app_sub_time between rec_lm.lm1_managed_start_date and  rec_lm.lm1_managed_end_date
and base.can_job_app_sub_time between rec_lm.lm2_managed_start_date and  rec_lm.lm2_managed_end_date

left join cte_linemanager_hierarchy hrm_lm 
on try_to_number(base.can_hiring_manager_external_id)=hrm_lm.workerid
and base.can_job_app_sub_time between hrm_lm.lm1_managed_start_date and  hrm_lm.lm1_managed_end_date
and base.can_job_app_sub_time between hrm_lm.lm2_managed_start_date and  hrm_lm.lm2_managed_end_date

full outer join cte_d_candidate_job job
on base.can_job_id=job.job_id

left join cte_d_office office 
on trim(split_part(job.job_primary_location_external_id,'-',2))=office.wd_loc_id

left join cte_office_mapping_country_only off_coo
    ON job.job_primary_location_external_id = off_coo.office_in_rdm_

,cte_d_candidate_stages as (
    select * from {{source("edm_recruiting_rpt","d_candidate_stages")}}
)

,cte_candidate_stages_bin as (
    select 
        stg.can_application_id,
        stg.can_prev_stage,
        bins.bins_approved,
        bins.bins_order        
    from cte_d_candidate_stages stg left join
    cte_stage_bins bins on stg.can_prev_stage = bins.current_stages
)

,cte_profile_bin_tag as (
    select 
        can_application_id,
        1 as IS_APPLY,
        IFNULL(MAX(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED IN ('assessment') THEN 1 ELSE NULL END),0) as IS_ASSESSMENT,
        IFNULL(MAX(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED IN ('screen') THEN 1 ELSE NULL END),0) as IS_SCREEN,
        IFNULL(MAX(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED IN ('interview') THEN 1 ELSE NULL END),0) as IS_INTERVIEW,
        IFNULL(MAX(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED IN ('Offer Extend') THEN 1 ELSE NULL END),0) as IS_OE,
        -- IFNULL(MAX(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED IN ('pre-hire') THEN 1 ELSE NULL END),0) as IS_PH,
        IFNULL(MAX(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED IN ('Offer Accept') THEN 1 ELSE NULL END),0) as IS_OA,
        IFNULL(MAX(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED IN ('reject') THEN 1 ELSE NULL END),0) as IS_REJECT,
        IFNULL(MAX(CASE WHEN BINS_APPROVED IN ('pre-hire','hired') THEN 1 ELSE NULL END),0) as IS_HIRED
    from cte_candidate_stages_bin
    group by all
)

,cte_reject_stages_data_prep AS 
(
SELECT
    STG.CAN_APPLICATION_ID,
    STG.CAN_PREV_STAGE,
    BINS.BINS_APPROVED,
    LAG(STG.CAN_PREV_STAGE) 
        OVER (
            PARTITION BY STG.CAN_APPLICATION_ID
            ORDER BY STG.CAN_PREV_STAGETS ,BINS_ORDER
    ) AS CAN_STAGE_PRIOR_REJECTION,
    row_number() 
        over (
            PARTITION BY STG.CAN_APPLICATION_ID
        ORDER BY STG.CAN_PREV_STAGETS  desc, BINS_ORDER DESC
        ) as rn
FROM
cte_d_candidate_stages STG 
LEFT JOIN cte_stage_bins BINS 
ON STG.can_prev_stage=BINS.current_stages
qualify rn=1
order by STG.CAN_APPLICATION_ID DESC, STG.CAN_PREV_STAGETS DESC
)

,cte_prev_reject_stages AS (
    SELECT 
        *
    FROM cte_reject_stages_data_prep
    WHERE BINS_APPROVED ='reject'
)

, cte_profile_tags AS (
    SELECT
        CAN_PROFILE_ID,
        LISTAGG(DISTINCT CASE WHEN CAN_TAG_TYPE_NAME = 'user' THEN CAN_TAG_TEXT END, ', ') 
        AS user_source_tags,
        LISTAGG(DISTINCT CASE WHEN CAN_TAG_TYPE_NAME = 'system' THEN CAN_TAG_TEXT END, ', ') 
        AS system_source_tags,
        LISTAGG(DISTINCT CAN_TAG_TEXT, ', ') 
        AS all_tags
    FROM {{ref("d_candidate_profile_tags")}}
    GROUP BY CAN_PROFILE_ID
)
