    NVL(CAN_CURRENT_COMPANY,'-1'),'^', 
    NVL(CAN_USER_TAGS,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(CAN_SYSTEM_TAGS,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(CAN_ALL_TAGS,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(WD_POSITION_IDS,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(BST_ROLE,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(recruiting.WOR_JOB_SOURCER_WORKERID,'-1'), '^',
    NVL(recruiting.WOR_JOB_SOURCER_NAME,'-1'), '^',
    NVL(recruiting.WOR_JOB_RECRUITER_WORKERID,'-1'), '^',
    NVL(recruiting.WOR_JOB_RECRUITER_NAME,'-1'), '^',
    NVL(recruiting.WOR_JOB_RECRUITER_EMAIL,'-1'), '^',
    NVL(recruiting.WOR_JOB_PA_SPONSER_WORKERID,'-1'), '^',
    NVL(recruiting.WOR_JOB_PA_SPONSER_NAME,'-1'), '^',
    NVL(recruiting.WOR_HIRING_MANAGER_WORKERID,'-1'), '^',
    NVL(recruiting.WOR_HIRING_MANAGER_NAME,'-1'), '^',
    NVL(recruiting.WOR_HIRING_MANAGER_EMAIL,'-1'), '^',
    NVL(recruiting.WOR_JOB_OFFER_RECRUITER_WORKERID,'-1'), '^',
    NVL(recruiting.WOR_JOB_OFFER_RECRUITER_NAME,'-1'), '^',
    NVL(recruiting.WOR_JOB_OFFER_RECRUITER_EMAIL,'-1'), '^',
    NVL(recruiting.WOR_PROFILE_RECRUITER_WORKERID,'-1'), '^',
    NVL(recruiting.WOR_PROFILE_RECRUITER_NAME,'-1'), '^',
    NVL(recruiting.WOR_PROFILE_RECRUITER_EMAIL,'-1'), '^',
    NVL(recruiting.WOR_WORKERID,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(TARA_CAN_JOB_BUSINESS_UNIT,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(TARA_PRIMARY_ALLOCATION,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(TARA_SECONDARY_ALLOCATION,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(TARA_COSTALLOCATIONREGION_TM,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(TARA_CAN_OFFICE,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(TARA_CAN_REGION,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(COST_ALLOCATION_REGION,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(TARA_CAN_SYSTEM,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(TARA_CAN_SUBSYSTEM,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(TARA_CAN_COUNTRY,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(TARA_JOB_CATEGORY,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(TARA_JOB_PROFILE_FAMILY_GROUP,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(TARA_REPORTING_ORG,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(TARA_GENDER,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(TARA_BCG_X_CHAPTERS,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(TARA_COHORT,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(TARA_EMPLOYEE_TYPE,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(profile_tag.IS_APPLY,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(profile_tag.IS_ASSESSMENT,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(profile_tag.IS_SCREEN,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(profile_tag.IS_INTERVIEW,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(profile_tag.IS_OE,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(profile_tag.IS_OA,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(profile_tag.IS_REJECT,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(HIRED_FLAG,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(IS_START,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(reject_prev_stg.CAN_STAGE_PRIOR_REJECTION,'-1'),'^',
    NVL(IS_NATIVE,'-1'),'^'))),'^^^'))  as ROW_HASH_KEY
    -- recruiting.CAN_TAG_TEXT or recruiting.CAN_PROFILE_TAGS_COMBINED will come from cr360 mid april
from
cte_d_recruiting recruiting  
left join cte_d_candidate_experience can_exp
    on recruiting.can_profile_id=can_exp.can_profile_id
left join cte_profile_bin_tag profile_tag 
    on recruiting.can_application_id=profile_tag.can_application_id
left join cte_prev_reject_stages reject_prev_stg 
    on recruiting.can_application_id=reject_prev_stg.can_application_id
left join cte_gender lk_gender 
    on IFNULL(recruiting.can_pre_hire_gender,recruiting.can_profile_gender) = lk_gender.can_profile_gender
left join cte_allocation_mapping tm_alloc
    on  IFNULL(recruiting.CAN_JOB_OFFER_ALLOC1_NAME,recruiting.CAN_JOB_ALLOCATION1) = tm_alloc.allocation_union_rdm
left join cte_office_mapping_country_only off_coo
    ON TARA_CAN_OFFICE = off_coo.office_in_rdm_ 
left join cte_d_office d_office
    ON TARA_CAN_OFFICE =d_office.wd_loc_nm 
left join cte_stage_bins bins 
    ON recruiting.CAN_CURRENT_STAGE = bins.current_stages
left join cte_profile_tags tags
    ON recruiting.CAN_PROFILE_ID=tags.CAN_PROFILE_ID
left join cte_candidate_job job 
    ON job.job_id=recruiting.can_job_id

Model: d_candidate_communities_v
Schema: edm_recruiting_etl
Database: EDW_DEV_SGU
Materialization: view
Description: 
Depends On: source.dbt_recruiting.edw_candidate_rpt.d_candidate_communities, source.dbt_recruiting.edm_recruiting_rpt.d_worker, model.dbt_recruiting.d_candidate, model.dbt_recruiting.d_worker_work
SQL: {#
Jira         Date          Who                  Description
===================================================================================================================
GWHD-3947    2024/11/26    Kulvinder Singh     ORIGNAL CODE
#}
{{
    config(
        alias="d_candidate_communities_v",
        materialized="view",
        schema="edm_recruiting_etl",
        tags=["edm_recruiting_rpt", "edw_candidate_rpt"],
        copy_grants=true
    )
}}
-- depends_on: {{ ref('d_candidate') }}
-- depends_on: {{ ref('d_worker_work') }}
with
    cte_d_candidate_communities as (
        select {{dbt_utils.star(from=source("edw_candidate_rpt", "d_candidate_communities"), relation_alias="d_candidate_communities_view" ) }}
        from
            {{ source("edw_candidate_rpt", "d_candidate_communities") }} d_candidate_communities_view
    ),
    cte_active_worker as (
        select 
            workerid,
            preferedfirstname, 
            preferredlastname,
            trim(nvl(preferedfirstname,'')|| ' '|| nvl(preferredlastname,'')) as preferredname,
            primaryworkemailaddress 
        from {{ source("edm_recruiting_rpt", "d_worker") }}
        where worker_current_state_flag = 'Y'
    )

select 
    can.name,
    can.open,
    can.positionid,
    can.systemid,
    can.community_type,
    can.recruiter_external_id,
    wor.preferredname as wor_recruiter_name,
    wor.primaryworkemailaddress as wor_recruiter_email,
    can.pkhash_key,
    sha2(
        array_to_string(
            array_construct(
                to_varchar(nvl(can.name, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(can.open, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(can.positionid, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(can.systemid, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(can.community_type, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(can.recruiter_external_id, 'Y')),
                to_varchar(nvl(wor_recruiter_name, '-1')),
                to_varchar(nvl(wor_recruiter_email, '-1'))          
            ), 
            '^^^'
        )
    ) as row_hash_key
from cte_d_candidate_communities can
left join cte_active_worker  wor on nvl(try_to_number(can.recruiter_external_id),-1) =wor.workerid

name: d_candidate_eventteam_v
text:

Schema: edm_recruiting_etl

Description: 
Depends On: source.dbt_recruiting.edw_candidate_rpt.d_candidate_eventteam_data, source.dbt_recruiting.edm_recruiting_rpt.d_worker, model.dbt_recruiting.d_candidate, model.dbt_recruiting.d_worker_work
SQL: {#
Jira         Date          Who                  Description
===================================================================================================================
GWHD-3???    2025/08/25    Sumit Gupta     ORIGNAL CODE
#}
{{
    config(
        alias="d_candidate_eventteam_v",
        materialized="view",
        schema="edm_recruiting_etl",
        tags=["edm_recruiting_rpt", "edw_candidate_rpt"],
        copy_grants=true
    )
}}
-- depends_on: {{ ref('d_candidate') }}
-- depends_on: {{ ref('d_worker_work') }}
with
    cte_d_candidate_eventteam_data as (
        select {{dbt_utils.star(from=source("edw_candidate_rpt", "d_candidate_eventteam_data"), relation_alias="d_candidate_eventteam_data_view" ) }}
        from
            {{ source("edw_candidate_rpt", "d_candidate_eventteam_data") }} d_candidate_eventteam_data_view
    ),
    cte_active_worker as (
        select 
            workerid,
            preferedfirstname, 
            preferredlastname,
            trim(nvl(preferedfirstname,'')|| ' '|| nvl(preferredlastname,'')) as preferredname,
            primaryworkemailaddress 
        from {{ source("edm_recruiting_rpt", "d_worker") }}
        where worker_current_state_flag = 'Y'
    ),
    cte_joined as (
        select
            -- all event-team columns (except original ROW_HASH_KEY)
            c.eventteam_planned_event_id,
            c.eventteam_external_id,
            wor5.preferredname           as eventteam_name,
            wor5.primaryworkemailaddress as eventteam_email,
            c.eventteam_role,
            c.eventeam_added_by_external_id,
            wor6.preferredname           as eventteam_added_by_name,
            wor6.primaryworkemailaddress as eventteam_added_by_email,
            c.eventteam_title,
            c.eventteam_location,
            c.eventteam_profile_enc_id,
            c.eventteam_roles,                      -- ARRAY
            c.eventteam_status,
            c.eventteam_user_cal_event_id,
            c.eventteam_team_id,
            c.eventteam_team_name,
            c.eventteam_team_type,
            c.eventteam_perms,                      -- VARIANT
            c.dwh_last_updated,
            c.pkhash_key
        from edw_candidate_rpt.d_candidate_eventteam_data c
        -- If workerid is NUMBER and external IDs are VARCHAR, cast safely
        left join cte_active_worker wor5
            on try_to_number(c.eventteam_external_id) = wor5.workerid
        left join cte_active_worker wor6
            on try_to_number(c.eventeam_added_by_external_id) = wor6.workerid
        )

select
    cte_joined.*,
    -- Hash includes ALL projected columns (event-team fields + links + resolved worker fields)
    sha2(
      array_to_string(
        array_construct(
          -- event-team fields
          to_varchar(coalesce(to_varchar(eventteam_planned_event_id), '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(eventteam_external_id, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(eventteam_role, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(eventeam_added_by_external_id, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(eventteam_title, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(eventteam_location, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(eventteam_profile_enc_id, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(to_varchar(eventteam_roles), '-1')),      -- ARRAY -> string
          to_varchar(coalesce(eventteam_status, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(eventteam_user_cal_event_id, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(eventteam_team_id, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(eventteam_team_name, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(eventteam_team_type, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(to_varchar(eventteam_perms), '-1')),      -- VARIANT -> string
          to_varchar(coalesce(to_varchar(dwh_last_updated), '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(pkhash_key, '-1')),
          -- resolved worker fields for event-team
          to_varchar(coalesce(eventteam_name, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(eventteam_email, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(eventteam_added_by_name, '-1')),
          to_varchar(coalesce(eventteam_added_by_email, '-1'))
        ),
        '^^^'
      )
    ) as row_hash_key
from cte_joined

name: d_worker_hire_hist_v
text:
Model: d_worker_hire_hist_v
Schema: edm_recruiting_etl
Database: EDW_DEV_SGU
Materialization: view
Description: 
Depends On: source.dbt_recruiting.edm_recruiting_rpt.d_worker, model.dbt_recruiting.d_worker_work
SQL: {#
Jira         Date          Who                  Description
===================================================================================================================
GWHD-2545    2024/08/06    Kulvinder Singh     Orignal Code
#}
{{
    config(
        alias="D_WORKER_HIRE_HIST_V",
        materialized="view",
        schema="edm_recruiting_etl",
        tags=["edm_recruiting_rpt", "edw_worker_rpt"],
        copy_grants=true,
    )
}}

-- depends_on: {{ ref('d_worker_work') }}

with
    cte_worker_hire_dt_ranked as (
        select
            workerid,
            workerwid,
            workertype,
            hiredt,
            rec_start_date,
            rec_end_date,
            current_flag,
            pkhash,
            row_number() over (
                partition by workerid, workerwid, hiredt order by rec_start_date
            ) as rn
        from {{ source("edm_recruiting_rpt", "d_worker") }}
        where hiredt is not null
        order by workerid, hiredt, rec_start_date
    ),

    cte_worker_hire_dt_unique as (
        select * exclude(rn) from cte_worker_hire_dt_ranked where rn = 1
    ),

    cte_worker_filter as (
        select workerid, count(*)
        from cte_worker_hire_dt_unique
        group by workerid
        having count(*) > 1
    )

select
    workerid,
    workerwid,
    workertype,
    hiredt,
    rec_start_date as hire_eff_start_date,
    dateadd(
        second,
        -1,
        lead(rec_start_date, 1, '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000') over (
            partition by workerid order by hiredt
        )
    ) as hire_eff_end_date,
    case
        when
            (
                hire_eff_start_date <= current_timestamp()
                and hire_eff_end_date > current_timestamp()
            )
        then 'Y'
        else 'N'
    end as current_flag,
    sha2(
        array_to_string(
            array_construct(to_varchar(concat(workerid, '^', workerwid, '^', hiredt))),
            '^^^'
        )
    ) as pkhash,
    sha2(
        array_to_string(
            array_construct(
                to_varchar(
                    concat(
                        nvl(workerid, '-1'),
                        '^',
                        nvl(workerwid, '-1'),
                        '^',
                        nvl(workertype, '-1'),
                        '^',
                        nvl(hire_eff_start_date, '1-JAN-1900'),
                        '^',
                        nvl(hire_eff_end_date, '1-JAN-1900'),
                        '^',
                        nvl(current_flag, '-1'),
                        '^',
                        nvl(pkhash, '-1')
                    )
                )
            ),
            '^^^'
        )
    ) as row_hash_key
from cte_worker_hire_dt_unique
where workerid in (select workerid from cte_worker_filter)
